{"type": "article", "id": 35094, "title": "收了这只螃蟹，它能助你一钳之力｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-30T23:10:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35381, "name": "Kikkerland"}, {"id": 35382, "name": "PHAIdesign"}, {"id": 35383, "name": "Rumpl"}, {"id": 35384, "name": "Ravean"}, {"id": 35385, "name": "Power Practical"}, {"id": 35386, "name": "Vanessa Brokstad"}, {"id": 35387, "name": "Amanda Mohlin Stuart"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161201064353E7sSO1ozeydTnZxG.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Crab Mulit Tool by Kikkerland</h3><p>出门在外难免会碰到一些繁琐的小活需要解决，设计品牌 <a href=\"https://kikkerland.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kikkerland</a> 就将一些你可能会用到的工具制作成了迷你版，并将它们组合在了一起。这款名为 Crab Multi Tool 囊括了剪刀、开瓶/罐器、螺丝刀、小刀和绳锯，可以在你需要的时候助你一“钳”之力。这是它的<a href=\"https://kikkerland.com/collections/new/products/crab-multi-tool\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 20 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182622AieHsIuy1FwXP0Kl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182622v40aR2H5psBrNX1m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182622tal8Lo4XcPeERxnr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>十四面体年历 by PHAIdesign</h3><p>2016 年只剩下一个月了，有关年历的设计我们最近也提了不少，比如可以把玩的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/34082.html\">十二面体木制日历</a> DodeCal。PHAIdesign 最近也带来了一款打破平面日历呈现形式的日历，在对比不同类型的多面体之后，设计师最终选择了十四面体：其中十二面是日历，另外两面就成了底座和开口，为它增加了收纳的功能。这些日历上的字符均采用蚀刻工艺加工，并且特意采用了三种不同的刻画深度以增强 3D 立体感。这是它的<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c.w5003-15572245270.1.kTbyR4&amp;id=542144532838\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 198 元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182646owHqh57KaEGAu02J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.681579\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182646m6XhLYrZitRoWbf7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593421\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182646NXGhWwUP2yqVoz6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182647fhASKkBaUluZnT6C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Rumpl Puffe- by Rumpl, Ravean &amp; Power Practical</h3><p>又到了翻出暖床利器电热毯的时候了，你是不是也有想过在室外也能拥有一张温暖的被窝？为了突破传统电热毯的限制，户外用品品牌 <a href=\"http://gorumpl.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rumpl</a>、<a href=\"http://ravean.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ravean</a> 以及研发能源产品的 <a href=\"http://powerpractical.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Power Practical</a> 联手推出了一款通过电池供暖的毯子。Rumpl Puffe- 的外形和常见的睡垫颇为相似，采用防水且支持机洗的轻质面料。内置的移动电源由 Power Practical 提供，它既能为电热毯供电，也可以用来给随身携带的设备充电。由 Ravean 开发的碳加热系统能够在几秒内完成加热，最高可以达到 30 度。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rumpl/the-rumpl-puffe-a-portable-battery-powered-heated\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，自然和合成材料填充版的最低价分别为 199 和 299 美元，移动电源的价格为 40 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182717DKHgQALb81um5z7Z.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182716qOGDWKZnJw0VzBeE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130182716KCmW0daYH6rhjgu4.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.385294\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611301827166rtnCJSlYzi1safp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>PowerWatch by Matrix Industries</h3><p>来自美国的 <a href=\"http://www.matrixindustries.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matrix Industries</a> 是一个创立于 2011 年的设计团队，联合创始人之一的 Akram Boukai 自 2003 年起就在研究热能发电技术，这款名为 PowerWatch 的智能手表就是他带领团队研发的第一件产品。有别于普通的智能手表，它依赖内置的热能发电机运作，通过肌肤和表面温度之间差异产生能量。当手表摘下后，它会自动进入睡眠模式，加上内部电池所储存的能量，并不会影响正常运作。PowerWatch 涵盖了追踪卡路里消耗、监测睡眠质量和运动数据等常见的智能手表功能，所有的信息都可以通过配套的应用同步到手机。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/smartwatch-powered-by-you-matrix-powerwatch-watch-fitness#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194833anuhz5IxPlQEKkC9.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194833xErlC5ecX2vW9wIp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743077\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194833S2cnTQNw1eIBsjrE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611301948339o86E2nmJjkOPqFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Clipse by Vanessa Brokstad</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>半夜醒来用手机作为光源难免会觉得有些刺眼，为了让人们拥有柔和且使用灵活的夜灯，设计师 Vanessa Brokstad 以月蚀为灵感带来了这款名为 Clipse 的概念设计。灯具的缺口可以放在配套的支架或是挂在家中的门把上，非单点式的光源能够有效减轻夜间对人眼的刺激，营造出一种温暖的气氛。Brokstad 为此还设计了配套的手机应用，可以进行调整灯光明暗和定时关灯的操作。深色的界面采用了和夜灯造型相同的风格，看起来直观清爽。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194905AW38lUmdExocbveQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194905AvrkC25waJBqNSW7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194904ZYpfG1V4zujNhxEv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194905vYiejFh0gutID27O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194905grpFDb6x0lMvK3PW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Luc &amp; Louna by Amanda Mohlin Stuart</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>这套看上去干干净净的巧克力包装是美国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.amandamohlindesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Amanda Mohlin Stuart</a> 为概念品牌 <a href=\"http://www.amandamohlindesign.com/#/luc-louna/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luc &amp; Louna</a> 所设计的。除了下方用来区分口味的色条之外，包装正面只有位于正中央的简笔画涂鸦和三边标注的基本信息。纸盒反面，详细的成分被规规矩矩地写进了表格当中，延续了整体的简约风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194928nmwX8vCZe350UYAl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.481429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194928Spc6XAYUDir4HPVj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194928U0jPpgLNvRrkVfb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194928eZbDONksz4cKfwi7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194929AV64TfYeuZwgxMrp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161130194929Bk5zd2g03ayDMTnl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}